The paper focuses on age of information in a wireless network setting, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The proposed transmission scheme involves local cooperation between nodes, which is a topic related to distributed systems (cs.DS) and social networks (cs.SI). The paper also presents a scaling analysis, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG).
